Revision history for Perl extension FileDirUtil.

0.04	Sat 24 Aug 2019
	- add Travis CI
	- remove vintage CPAN links

0.03  Sun May 28 2017
	- $self->odir now accepts a Path::Class::Dir object or an ArrayRef of path
		segments that will be coerced into a Path::Class::Dir object

0.02  Tue May 23 2017
	- provide set_ifilebn() method

0.01  Sun May 14 2017
	- initial release
